## 2026-03-28 - PublishPanel retry loop catches all errors as timeout retries
- Fixed the orphan deletion retry loop to distinguish timeout errors from non-timeout errors. Previously the bare `catch {}` block silently retried all errors (malformed messages, plugin crashes, etc.) as if they were timeouts. Now only `Error('Timeout')` triggers retry with escalating timeouts; any other error is immediately surfaced via `setReadinessError` using `describeError()`.
- Files changed: `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/components/PublishPanel.tsx` ~L204-212
- **Learnings for future iterations:**

